WEBVTT

00:00.600 --> 00:03.600
<i>Previously on Medium:
Good God Almighty.</i>

00:04.030 --> 00:05.250
He's got it all here.

00:05.500 --> 00:07.699
When school starts, when school gets out,

00:07.700 --> 00:09.750
clubs they go to, friends' houses.

00:10.140 --> 00:13.500
I want a detail on that house 24 hours a day until we find this lunatic.

00:13.503 --> 00:14.849
This is Allison Dubois.

00:14.850 --> 00:16.900
And this is Lucas Harvey.

00:17.130 --> 00:18.200
What do you want?

00:18.740 --> 00:22.990
God has a plan, and there's no room in it for prophets.

00:23.150 --> 00:24.500
For seers.

00:24.503 --> 00:28.450
You and the Almighty will be discussing it face to face.

00:31.300 --> 00:32.650
It's holy water.

00:32.750 --> 00:34.300
To cleanse you with.

